title.rendered: If you are not a DEXT holder yet, discover what you’re missing out! DEXT Utility Token

content.rendered:
Discover our Standard Tier!

Are you a user but not a holder? Discover 1000 DEXT Standard Tier!

Did you know all the features you have at your disposal if you are a 1,000 DEXT holder, by simply connecting your wallet on DEXTools?

  • Our Standard Subscription Tier can be obtained by holding 1,000 DEXT tokens, and offers a range of exclusive features for traders aiming to elevate their DeFi trading experience.

Some of the unique benefits unlocked with this standard plan subscription include:

  • No Limit Favourite Pairs: Create custom favorites lists with an unlimited number of tokens and filter them with folders.
  • My Positions (P&L Tracker): Track and monitor profits and losses in real time.
  • Trade Analytics: Easily monitor and analyze your portfolio by viewing the number of buys, sells, average price, and date of the swap for each coin.
  • Wallet Info & Tracker: Add up to 500 wallets and check their trade history, an essential tool for tracking successful traders’ movements.
  • Desktop/Mail/Telegram Price Alerts: Set customized notifications for specific asset price thresholds, keeping you informed about market movements and potential trading opportunities.
  • No Advertisement: Enjoy an ad-free experience while using DEXTools.
  • 12 Hot Pairs: Access a higher number of the most visited pairs in the last 24 hours.
  • Limit Order and Trading Bot: Set specific buy/sell orders at desired prices and automate trades, improving efficiency and accuracy in trading strategies.

 

This is how the exclusive perks are shown!

 

 

 

 

 

Dext Force HQ

 

Apart from these captivating features, there is an additional incentive to hold 1,000 $DEXT tokens: the privilege of gaining entry to the exclusive Telegram group reserved for 1000 $DEXT token holders

Join the community connecting your wallet with 1000 $DEXT to the Dext Force bot now!: https://t.me/dextForce_bot?start=pprem_dd377c7e-e44d-493b-a78d-1c6d75cfaf8b

Benefits of joining the Telegram group

 

By becoming a member of this group, you can gain entry to a diverse and lively community consisting of individuals who possess a strong enthusiasm for the realm of DeFi.

  • This group aims to foster an environment where like-minded DeFi enthusiasts can come together to share valuable insights, up-to-date information, thought-provoking discussions, and extensive knowledge pertaining to this dynamic and rapidly progressing domain.

 

When you join the group, you will have the opportunity to avail yourself of various enticing benefits, including:

  • Alpha leaks and trading insights: Gain exclusive access to insider information on upcoming DeFi projects and acquire valuable insights into the most recent trends shaping the industry.
  • News: Keep yourself informed and in the loop regarding the latest advancements in the DeFi realm through real-time news updates, comprehensive market analysis, and much more.
  • Degen chat: Engage with fellow DeFi enthusiasts who share similar interests and actively participate in discussions about the newest trends, projects, and trading strategies in the field.
  • NFTs chat: Join forces with fellow NFT traders who share your adventurous spirit, enabling you to stay ahead of the curve by never missing out on the latest hyped releases or discovering undervalued projects.
  • Support: In case you encounter any platform-related issues, simply reach out for assistance in the dedicated section, and rest assured that you will receive prompt support in resolving your concerns.

 

 

You’ll also get the opportunity to network with industry experts, participate in exclusive events and giveaways. With so many incentives, it’s easy to see why joining the 1000 $DEXT holder’s Telegram group is a no-brainer for DeFi enthusiasts.
